Betsy King Ross https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Betsy_King_Ross 0 Betsy King Ross (March 14, 1921 – October 4, 1989) was an American actress, anthropologist and author.She was born in St Paul, Minnesota. During the 1930s she starred in several Western serial films as a child actress. In 1935 she starred with Gene Autry in the serial The Phantom Empire. She was also a champion trick rider.
